---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Motos Elegibles" currentPage="motos">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-racing-black via-racing-gray to-racing-black"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-racing-green text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 block">Tu Moto Encaja</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 text-white" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
          Motos <span class="text-vanilla">Elegibles</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-racing-silver leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
          Motos 125cc de serie. Sin ventajas injustas, sin presupuestos infinitos.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-vanilla font-semibold">
          El piloto importa más que la moto
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Motos Permitidas Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-racing-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-vanilla text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Motos Homologadas</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Encuentra <span class="text-vanilla">tu moto</span></h2>
        <p class="text-racing-silver text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Todas las 125cc de 4 tiempos (115-125cc) o 2 tiempos (máx. 50cc) homologadas para circular son válidas.
          <br/>
          <span class="text-vanilla font-semibold">Tu moto está lista. Tú decides cuándo.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- ¿Tu moto no está? Card - Featured -->
        <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-racing-green/10 to-racing-black/80 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-dashed border-racing-green/40 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center group hover:border-racing-green/70 hover:bg-racing-green/15 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-racing-green/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-racing-green/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-racing-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-vanilla mb-3" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;">¿Tu moto encaja?</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Si tu 125cc de serie cumple con las especificaciones, ya estás listo para correr.
          </p>
          <a href="/reglamento" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-racing-green hover:text-racing-green-light font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm transition-colors">
            Ver Requisitos
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Yamaha YZF-R125 / MT-125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Yamaha-YZF-R125-MT-125.png" alt="Yamaha YZF-R125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Yamaha YZF-R125 / MT-125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más redonda y eficaz, la referencia para ir rápido con facilidad.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2008–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- KTM RC 125 / 125 Duke -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/KTM-RC-125-Duke.png" alt="KTM RC 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">KTM RC 125 / 125 Duke</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La de más aplomo, por frenada y rigidez.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2010–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Kawasaki Ninja 125 / Z125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Kawasaki-Ninja-125-Z125.png" alt="Kawasaki Ninja 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Kawasaki Ninja 125 / Z125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más estable y predecible, da mucha confianza para ser constante y rápido.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2018–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Suzuki GSX-R125 / GSX-S125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Suzuki-GSX-R125-GSX-S125.png" alt="Suzuki GSX-R125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Suzuki GSX-R125 / GSX-S125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más ligera y ágil, imbatible en cambios de dirección.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2017–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Honda CBR125R / CB125R -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Honda-CBR125R-CB125R.png" alt="Honda CBR125R" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Honda CBR125R / CB125R</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más premium y fina, por tacto de calidad y parte ciclo muy completa.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2004–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Aprilia RS4 125 / Tuono 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Aprilia-RS4-125-Tuono-125.png" alt="Aprilia RS4 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Aprilia RS4 125 / Tuono 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más racing en sensaciones, con una conducción más "directa" y de deportiva que la media.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2011–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Derbi GPR 125 4T -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Derbi-GPR-125-4T.png" alt="Derbi GPR 125 4T" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Derbi GPR 125 4T</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más de "escuela R", por postura y reacciones.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2009–2014</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Rieju RS3 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Rieju-RS3-125.png" alt="Rieju RS3 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Rieju RS3 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más simple y directa, con comportamiento fácil de leer y de llevar al límite.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2012–2016</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Malaguti RST 125 / Drakon 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Malaguti-RST-125-Drakon-125.png" alt="Malaguti RST 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Malaguti RST 125 / Drakon 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más compacta, ideal para circuitos pequeños y ratoneros.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2019–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Voge 125R -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Voge-125R.png" alt="Voge 125R" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Voge 125R</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más aplomada de la nueva generación, transmite seguridad y estabilidad en apoyo.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2023–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- QJ Motor SRK 125R -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/QJ-Motor-SRK-125R.png" alt="QJ Motor SRK 125R" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">QJ Motor SRK 125R</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más nerviosa de dirección, rápida de girar y reactiva en cambios de apoyo.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2024–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Zontes U125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Zontes-U125.png" alt="Zontes U125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Zontes U125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más amable y progresiva, fácil de llevar rápido sin sustos.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2021–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Keeway RKF 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Keeway-RKF-125.png" alt="Keeway RKF 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Keeway RKF 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más fácil y dócil, muy buena para construir ritmo y técnica.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2018–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- MITT GP2 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/MITT-GP2-125.png" alt="MITT GP2 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">MITT GP2 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La única con doble disco delantero. Tacto sport con sensaciones de "R" al descolgarte.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2023–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- MBP / Morbidelli F125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/MBP-Morbidelli-F125.png" alt="MBP Morbidelli F125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">MBP / Morbidelli F125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más neutra, estable y sencilla de coger ritmo y repetir vueltas.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2025–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Daelim Roadwin 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Daelim-Roadwin-125.png" alt="Daelim Roadwin 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Daelim Roadwin 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más clásica y noble, reacciones suaves y previsibles.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2004–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Kymco Quannon 125 / Quannon Naked -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Kymco-Quannon-125.png" alt="Kymco Quannon 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Kymco Quannon 125 / Naked</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más tranquila y estable. Blandita, para ir por el sitio sin pelea.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2007–2012</p>
        </div>

        <!-- CFMOTO 125NK -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/CFMOTO-125NK.png" alt="CFMOTO 125NK" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">CFMOTO 125NK</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más firme de chasis entre las nuevas, con buena sensación de aplomo.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2025–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bajaj Pulsar NS125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Bajaj-Pulsar-NS125.png" alt="Bajaj Pulsar NS125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Bajaj Pulsar NS125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más robusta y constante, aguanta bien el trato y mantiene ritmo sin complicaciones.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2021–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- SYM Wolf 125i -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/SYM-Wolf-125i.png" alt="SYM Wolf 125i" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">SYM Wolf 125i</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más ligera y simple, perfecta para trazar y buscar paso por curva.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2019–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FB Mondial Piega 125 -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/FB-Mondial-Piega-125.png" alt="FB Mondial Piega 125" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">FB Mondial Piega 125</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más deportiva de tacto, con una conducción más "tensa" y precisa que muchas alternativas.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2022–presente</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Hyosung GT125R / GT125 Comet -->
        <div class="card group relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-racing-green text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">125cc</div>
          <div class="aspect-video bg-racing-black rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-racing-silver/10 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/motos/Hyosung-GT125R-Comet.png" alt="Hyosung GT125R" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Hyosung GT125R / Comet</h3>
          <p class="text-racing-silver text-sm mb-4">La más diferente, por ser bicilíndrica y tener presencia de moto grande.</p>
          <p class="text-vanilla text-xs font-semibold">2001–2016</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-racing-black via-racing-gray to-racing-black overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-racing-green rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 text-white" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
          ¿Tu <span class="text-vanilla">Moto</span> está lista?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-racing-silver leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
          Consulta el reglamento técnico para confirmar que tu moto cumple las especificaciones y conocer las modificaciones permitidas.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
          <a href="/reglamento" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-10 py-5 inline-flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
            Ver Reglamento Técnico
          </a>
